{"tid":818274,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋會吹斷嗎？","createTime":"2018-09-14T04:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T06:20:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"90a1c558849fe83a6cd334da2f6b24cee4a58200","tid":818274,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20180914/20498819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20498819&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=262114b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20498819&h=c6410460\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20180914/20498819</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月14日 <br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋會吹斷嗎？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180914/large/1536829392_ea3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180914%2Flarge%2F1536829392_ea3d.jpg&h=44efe101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n昨天說中世紀術士為了追求知識，可以去到召喚魔鬼咁盡。據古書所載，惡魔現形，術士會問魔鬼「風在哪兒，從哪兒來」（ubi est ventus　&amp; unde veniat）；如果是我，大概會問「颱風」一詞從哪兒來。<br />\n<br />\n中國古代沒有「颱」字，以我所知，最早收錄「颱」的文獻見於清代，例如王士禛《香祖筆記》、俞正燮《癸巳類稿》等。王士禛說：「臺灣風信與他海殊異，風大而烈者為颶，又甚者為颱。」俞正燮說雞籠山（即今天九份基隆山）有「識颱草」，「一節則一年一颱汛，無節則其年無颱」，並注明：「颱，大具風也。」（具，即颶）俞正燮要特地加注，可見「颱」不是常用字。 <br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，「颱風」英文是「typhoon」，兩者音近。我不解的是：到底「颱風」是「typhoon」的音譯，像「幽默」來自「humour」？抑或「typhoon」來自「颱風」，像「ketchup」來自「茄汁」？<br />\n<br />\n牛津字典編者猜測，「typhoon」可能來自中文「tai fung」，即大風。我自己則傾向相信，「typhoon」來自古希臘文「Typhon」，即古希臘神話的巨人堤豐，也是暴風之神。最困惑的是，各種猜測都能自圓其說，從哪個方向想也說得通。 <br />\n<br />\n同樣困惑的問題：風王之王山竹後日襲港，到底該把港珠澳大橋吹塌好，抑或不吹塌好？根據權威的中央氣象台估計，山竹風力可達超強颱風級別的17級；日前某份公信力甚高的左報則說，「港珠澳大橋的設計，能抗16級颱風、7級地震，設計壽命長達120年」。<br />\n<br />\n能抗16級颱風的大橋，遇上17級的山竹，勢必夭折，但既是「百年一遇」，自然也沒有人需要負責。大橋若能上承天意、下應民心地塌下來，建築商應該最高興，再賺一千億不是夢；假如不塌下來，坦白說，更令人害怕了。大橋被山竹衝擊一次，恐怕唔死都重傷，想逐漸冧又得，即刻冧晒亦得。<br />\n<br />\n即刻冧，政府花多千億；逐漸冧，可能死傷枕藉。從哪個方向想都沒有出路。今日香港再也受不起考驗，山竹還是不要來吧。  <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾 <br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n逃稅天堂 (邁克)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n天災人禍現形記 (蔣芸)"},{"pid":"a850a1d158afc5fb39b14465bf9741b1647ec462","tid":818274,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:08:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">新起架喎 </span></span>"},{"pid":"e9cafb3751bac399c024c5332ef69626bf8abb2b","tid":818274,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"期待"},{"pid":"b152ab1212d6969aec83c3220464c6251086ee93","tid":818274,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a850a1d158afc5fb39b14465bf9741b1647ec462","tid":818274,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:08:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">新起架喎 </span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:03:18.000Z","msg":"個風百年一遇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e951854ce099108f33ca0ed98cabbc2e5c683c","tid":818274,"uid":116910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b152ab1212d6969aec83c3220464c6251086ee93","tid":818274,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a850a1d158afc5fb39b14465bf9741b1647ec462","tid":818274,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:08:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">新起架喎 </span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:03:18.000Z","msg":"個風百年一遇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"但係橋設計係 120年喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次個風起碼都萬年一遇啦"},{"pid":"3bade63debf83ff70aa6c302addae5e4162411d8","tid":818274,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"青馬大橋吸水門橋汀九橋昂船洲大橋頂到幾多級"},{"pid":"ea85ea28e3dd40288999c856ffa1d605abbec343","tid":818274,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔斷，會成條沉"},{"pid":"d2f28aec529d29cc28bdb73174ff77c3de0f6afc","tid":818274,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"斷就唔會，但可能飃移"},{"pid":"39612374269ef06577b2b1a6ee494108c4c638f5","tid":818274,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"大陸狗睇唔到個地方就一定會呃！就會偷工減料！橋唔會斷不過橋墩就....."},{"pid":"a2398e1aead0c2cc9d6a92ac13084f59f44d4270","tid":818274,"uid":90060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w68-7QlygME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw68-7QlygME&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=97d1d318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w68-7QlygME</a>"},{"pid":"e2803d8b913f8439a32e6a3e6d03dda678028fa4","tid":818274,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"唔會即斷，但之後用就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"c8ad166f8afd7f5c998b76cf8a25ca75743eecf8","tid":818274,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2398e1aead0c2cc9d6a92ac13084f59f44d4270","tid":818274,"uid":90060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w68-7QlygME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw68-7QlygME&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLf